-= Kitchen =-

The counter is vast. Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the counter. You make out a stove. The stove is conventional. Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. Hopefully this doesn't make you too upset.

-= Kitchen =-
You arrive in a kitchen. A standard one.

Look over there! a fridge. You idly wonder how they came up with the name TextWorld for this place. It's pretty fitting. The fridge contains a raw pork chop. You see a closed oven. You can make out a table. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a table? The table is massive. On the table you can make out a cookbook and a knife. You see a counter. The counter is vast. Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the counter. You make out a stove. The stove is conventional. Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. Hopefully this doesn't make you too upset.

Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. Hopefully this doesn't make you too upset.

-= Kitchen =-
You arrive in a kitchen. A standard one.

Look over there! a fridge. You idly wonder how they came up with the name TextWorld for this place. It's pretty fitting. The fridge contains a raw pork chop. You see a closed oven. You can make out a table. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a table? The table is massive. On the table you can make out a cookbook and a knife. You see a counter. The counter is vast. Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the counter. You make out a stove. The stove is conventional. Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. Hopefully this doesn't make you too upset.

Look over there! a fridge. You idly wonder how they came up with the name TextWorld for this place. It's pretty fitting. The fridge contains a raw pork chop. You see a closed oven. You can make out a table. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a table? The table is massive. On the table you can make out a cookbook and a knife. You see a counter. The counter is vast. Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the counter. You make out a stove. The stove is conventional. Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. Hopefully this doesn't make you too upset.

Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. Hopefully this doesn't make you too upset.

You are hungry! Let's cook a delicious meal. Check the cookbook in the kitchen for the recipe. Once done, enjoy your meal!

-= Kitchen =-
You arrive in a kitchen. A standard one.

Look over there! a fridge. You idly wonder how they came up with the name TextWorld for this place. It's pretty fitting. The fridge contains a raw pork chop. You see a closed oven. You can make out a table. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a table? The table is massive. On the table you can make out a cookbook and a knife. You see a counter. The counter is vast. Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the counter. You make out a stove. The stove is conventional. Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. Hopefully this doesn't make you too upset.

You are hungry! Let's cook a delicious meal. Check the cookbook in the kitchen for the recipe. Once done, enjoy your meal!

-= Kitchen =-
You arrive in a kitchen. A standard one.

Look over there! a fridge. You idly wonder how they came up with the name TextWorld for this place. It's pretty fitting. The fridge contains a raw pork chop. You see a closed oven. You can make out a table. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a table? The table is massive. On the table you can make out a cookbook and a knife. You see a counter. The counter is vast. Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the counter. You make out a stove. The stove is conventional. Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. Hopefully this doesn't make you too upset.
